"title": "9513: hell, as incentive to action",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "9513",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The reality of hell should affect the way people live.</p>\n<h2>The importance of making the right choice</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:13-Matt7:14\">MAT 7:13–7:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:19\">DEU 30:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer21:8\">JER 21:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:23-Luke13:25\">LUK 13:23–13:25</a></p>\n<h2>A personal spiritual life is vital</h2>\n<h3>It is more important than short-term worldly gain</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:26\">MAT 16:26</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:36\">MRK 8:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:25\">LUK 9:25</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:20\">LUK 12:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:19-Luke16:25\">LUK 16:19–16:25</a></p>\n<h3>It is not just outward appearance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:7-Matt3:10\">MAT 3:7–3:10</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:7-Luke3:9\">LUK 3:7–3:9</a></p>\n<h3>Religious activity alone is not only valueless but perilous</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:21-Matt7:23\">MAT 7:21–7:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:12\">PRO 14:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:11-Jer23:12\">JER 23:11–23:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:26-Luke13:28\">LUK 13:26–13:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:6\">JHN 15:6</a></p>\n<h2>Believers must maintain their loyalty to God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:28\">MAT 10:28</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:4-Luke12:5\">LUK 12:4–12:5</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:23-Deut4:24\">DEU 4:23–4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:12-Isa8:13\">ISA 8:12–8:13</a></p>\n<h2>Temptations to sin must be dealt with drastically</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:29-Matt5:30\">MAT 5:29–5:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:8-Matt18:9\">MAT 18:8–18:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:43-Mark9:48\">MRK 9:43–9:48</a></p>\n<h2>Some attitudes and practices that lead to hell</h2>\n<h3>Deliberately continuing in sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:26-Heb10:27\">HEB 10:26–10:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:30\">NUM 15:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:4-Heb6:6\">HEB 6:4–6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:20\">2PE 2:20</a></p>\n<h3>Lack of spiritual response</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:13\">MAT 22:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:51\">MAT 24:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:30\">MAT 25:30</a></p>\n<h3>Wilfully ignoring divine activity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:20-Matt11:24\">MAT 11:20–11:24</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:13-Luke10:15\">LUK 10:13–10:15</a> <em>Sodom, destroyed by God, was notoriously sinful.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:33\">MAT 23:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:41-Matt25:46\">MAT 25:41–25:46</a></p>\n<h3>Contempt for fellow humans</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:22\">MAT 5:22</a></strong> <em>The term “fool” implied the despising of another as worthless and godless.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:6\">JAS 3:6</a></p>",
